name: Made-To-Order Genuine Swarovski Crystal Decoden iPhone 5 Case
description:
Everyone can use a little sparkle & gleam. All this glitz & twinkle can't help but get noticed. Shine on, baby!

This listing is for a made-to-order, super kawaii decoden iPhone 5 case. I use only genuine Swarovski crystal flatbacks, kawaii cabochons, pearl flat backs & a clear, ultra thin iPhone snap-on case backing that is made of a flexible plastic (if you would like to use a different case, please let me know). 100% of the crystals I use on my cases are genuine Swarovski crystals; no blending with cheaper rhinestones here! I use a super strong adhesive on all my cases but accidents do happen...which is why all of my cases come with an "ouchie pack" of extra crystals & pearls. Got a BlackBerry, Droid, etc? I'm open to doing these cases as well; convo me & let's talk!

Email me (zoeybaby808@gmail.com) with your likes (example: light pink, Hello Kitty, stars, hearts, pearls). After receiving your information, I will send you a layout of the materials I will be using for your personalized case. Once all the specifications have been confirmed by you, I'll get to work! You will receive your case within 2-3 weeks after I receive your payment.

I LOVE doing custom orders...pill cases, lighters, metal purse hooks, you name it! Message me & I'll create a custom listing for you. The possibilities are endless! 

NOTE: The cases in the pictures are only examples.

***FREE GIFT WITH PURCHASE!!!***

Shipping note: Shipping costs include packaging, U.S. Priority mail through USPS & delivery confirmation. If you would like your package to be sent with insurance, please leave a note with your order (additional shipping fees will be added to your total). I will not be held responsible for items that are damaged or lost & not covered by insurance.


Please "like" my page on Facebook for exclusive coupon codes & updates! http://www.facebook.com/Zoeybaby808
